data.description: Fisherman's paradise, home at last! Beautiful waterfront view from the largest parcel in the neighborhood, and no flood insurance needed! 4 Point home inspection and wind mitigation done in November 2023! New roof and HVAC system in 2022. Beautiful new vinyl plank flooring through out the home! Relax on the front porch with a wonderful breeze from the lake! Screened in back porch with a wood burning stove to enjoy on the cool winter nights! Bring your boat, park it in the covered parking area to keep it out of the weather! Public boat ramp in the neighborhood. A short drive to nearest hospital and local amenities. Call today for your personal tour.
